tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE cryptocurrency_transactions (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sender_address VARCHAR(255),
    receiver_address VARCHAR(255),
    amount DECIMAL,
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE cryptocurrency_transactions (
  transaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  sender_wallet_address VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  receiver_wallet_address VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  amount NUMERIC,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE cryptocurrency_transactions (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sender_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    recipient_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    amount DECIMAL(18, 2) NOT NULL,
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE transaction_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transaction_id INT NOT NULL,
    regulatory_agency_id INT NOT NULL,
    analysis_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    compliance_status BOOLEAN NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE transactions ( 
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    sender_address VARCHAR(255), 
    receiver_address VARCHAR(255), 
    amount DECIMAL(10, 2), 
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP 
);

CREATE TABLE accounts ( 
    account_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    account_name VARCHAR(255), 
    account_type VARCHAR(50), 
    balance DECIMAL(10, 2), 
    creation_date TIMESTAMP 
);

CREATE TABLE users ( 
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    username VARCHAR(50), 
    email VARCHAR(100), 
    country VARCHAR(100), 
    registration_date TIMESTAMP 
);

CREATE TABLE regulations ( 
    regulation_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    regulation_name VARCHAR(100), 
    regulator VARCHAR(100), 
    description TEXT, 
    effective_date DATE 
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sender_id INT,
    receiver_id INT,
    amount DECIMAL,
    date TIMESTAMP
);
